{"asctime": "2026-04-14T17:47:51Z", "levelname": "INFO", "name": "httpx", "message": "HTTP Request: POST https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages \"HTTP/1.1 200 OK\""}
{"asctime": "2026-04-14T17:47:51Z", "levelname": "INFO", "name": "infrastructure.ai.claude_session_tutor", "message": "Claude session tutor response received", "session_id": "sess_447c4b87668e", "elapsed_s": 5.05, "response_snippet": "\u00a1Genial, me alegra que est\u00e9s aqu\u00ed! \ud83c\udf89\n\nImagina que tienes una m\u00e1quina expendedora m\u00e1gica: le metes una moneda y **siempre** te da exactamente el mismo producto, sin importar nada m\u00e1s. Las funciones matem\u00e1ticas funcionan igual \u2014 les \"metes\" un n\u00famero y te dan otro n\u00famero de vuelta.\n\nAqu\u00ed va la pregunt", "usage": {"input_tokens": 598, "output_tokens": 154}}
{"asctime": "2026-04-14T17:47:51Z", "levelname": "INFO", "name": "persistence", "message": "Session saved", "session_id": "sess_447c4b87668e", "status": "active"}
