{"asctime": "2026-04-14T17:48:21Z", "levelname": "INFO", "name": "infrastructure.ai.claude_session_tutor", "message": "Calling Claude session tutor", "session_id": "sess_447c4b87668e", "gagne_event": 1, "ped_state": "demotivation", "message_count": 1}
{"asctime": "2026-04-14T17:48:24Z", "levelname": "INFO", "name": "httpx", "message": "HTTP Request: POST https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages \"HTTP/1.1 200 OK\""}
{"asctime": "2026-04-14T17:48:24Z", "levelname": "INFO", "name": "infrastructure.ai.claude_session_tutor", "message": "Claude session tutor response received", "session_id": "sess_447c4b87668e", "elapsed_s": 3.43, "response_snippet": "\u00a1Buena pregunta misteriosa! \ud83d\ude04\n\nImagina que tienes una m\u00e1quina m\u00e1gica: le metes el n\u00famero **8** y ella te escupe otro n\u00famero sin que t\u00fa hagas nada m\u00e1s. \u00bfQu\u00e9 crees que hace esa m\u00e1quina por dentro para transformarlo?\n\n\u00bfTe animas a descubrir c\u00f3mo funciona esa \"m\u00e1quina\"? \ud83d\udd27", "usage": {"input_tokens": 591, "output_tokens": 106}}
{"asctime": "2026-04-14T17:48:24Z", "levelname": "INFO", "name": "persistence", "message": "Session saved", "session_id": "sess_447c4b87668e", "status": "active"}
